#

Brussels Sprouts Salad with Apples and Walnuts

10 min
$8
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Tree nuts

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free option available

Cuisine:

American

Course:

SaladSide Dish

Tags:

saladhealthyquickno-cook

Description

A refreshing salad combining crunchy Brussels sprouts, sweet apples, and nutty walnuts, perfect for a quick and healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • brussels sprouts: 2 cups, thinly sliced
  • apple: 1, diced (preferably a sweet variety like Fuji or Honeycrisp)
  • walnuts: 1/2 cup, chopped
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
